{"tid":753332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川暴雨成災 港府賑災基金撥54萬買大米食油","createTime":"2018-07-23T13:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T14:05:17.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"546f008a200cf02fd3a96b828e26ed765bd91829","tid":753332,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"四川暴雨成災 港府賑災基金撥54萬買大米食油"},{"pid":"efc29d96957ac11b25e1e514cbf7be6d7de86bf7","tid":753332,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"四川省本月初至月中暴雨成災。網上截圖<br />\n四川省本月初至月中暴雨成災，綿陽市政府更指，這是當地1949年以來最大洪水。港府決定從賑災基金批出53萬6千元的撥款，予愛德基金會（香港）賑濟當地災民，款項會用於提供大米及食油，解決燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人今日表示，撥款是按賑災基金諮詢委員會設立的快速審批撥款申請機制批出。有關機制旨在加快處理撥款申請，讓救援機構能夠在災禍發生後第一時間進行首階段的賑災工作。<br />\n<br />\n發言人稱，為確保撥款用於指定用途，委員會將要求愛德基金會（香港）在完成賑災計畫後向委員會呈交評估報告及經審核的帳目。"},{"pid":"255314518437fdc23313e9743047c77b206fe7d6","tid":753332,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1272888/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1272888%2F&d=9QPT0drjuQgb%2FdNg2gLAoDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=81abf3e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1272888%2F&h=f9ba9aa8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1272888/</a>"},{"pid":"c40106cac77f42642dd4e161fde445d568ffc866","tid":753332,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180723/_2018072315173596108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180723%2F_2018072315173596108.jpg&h=fcfec7b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02389d4e9ed7de5d88ce3945181147d6cdce7c48","tid":753332,"uid":174601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score